net.sourceforge.sqlunit
Interface IErrorCodes

public interface IErrorCodes

This interface lists the generic error codes that are raised by SQLUnit. The documentation explains each of these errors in detail, including what corrective action to take.

Version:
$Revision: 1.43 $
Author:
Sujit Pal (spal@users.sourceforge.net)
